FBIS3-41915 "jptnd003___94074" JPRS-TND-93-003 Document Type:JPRS Document Title:PROLIFERATION ISSUES 31 January 1994 WEST EUROPE FRANCE Leotard Calls For Resumption of Nuclear Testing AU1001102994 Paris AFP in English 1004 GMT 10 Jan 94 AU1001102994 Paris AFP Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Paris, Jan 10 (AFP) -- France ought to resume nuclear weapons testing as soon as possible, Defence Minister Francois Leotard said here Monday [10 January], contradicting President Francois Mitterrand. Speaking in a radio interview, Leotard said the precise reason for resuming tests was to acquire simulation techniques. [passage omitted on Mitterand interview covered by referent item]
